{
  "stem": "11552.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I was on the fields there, I used to look mostly on fields where women worked, and I thought well, the women are not going to leave their fields and going to kill me or going to bring me to the police, so I would be fairly safe with them.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I never stayed more than a few hours, and then I went back into the forest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I stayed the night in the forest, and I continued with this little bit of bread, but it took me quite a few days to get back to Buczacz.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't talk much, I just worked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I got back to Buczacz, the first thing I did-- we had-- I knew a family, Pisarski.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to them and I asked for some food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told them that-- because my mother knew them too, they lived not far from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told them, in case my mother or my brother shows up, to tell them that I am in this area.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it is in-- then I left because they were so afraid for me to be seen there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First of all, they didn't believe that I was still alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They thought that I was some-- some kind of-- some kind of myth, or some-- or some shadow, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I left because I didn't want to endanger them, either.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, but my mother found out-- she came back, and she went to them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she found that I am in this area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then she was searching for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you imagine searching for somebody in the fields on the far-- in the villages?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is almost impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
